data.description: Introducing this charming 2 bedroom, 1 bath cozy home with a perfect blend of comfort and  character nestled on a serene street. Step inside and be greeted by a warm and inviting home  where modern upgrades meet classic charm. The large backyard is complete with a privacy  fence, shed, and firepit. It's the perfect spot for outdoor gatherings, creating memories, and  enjoying the cool evenings. Relax on the covered front porch, a lovely space to unwind after a  long day. Have peace of mind with newer electrical wiring, gutters, water heater and windows.  Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own this quaint home in a peaceful setting. Sellers willing to pay some closing concessions with strong offer.
